            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " properties determine which part of the scene’s coordinate space is visible in the view."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You specify the value using the unit coordinate space. The default value is "
